name: makesense
overview:
Are you looking for the perfect vacation and donâ€™t know where to head to? If that is indeed the case, a visit to this Indian startup might just provide a breath of fresh air.

Broadly speaking, through this site you will be able to conduct a search of cities spanning the whole globe. Once you submit the name of the city in question, you will be presented with a Google Map that will let you watch it in finer detail, whereas a collection of photographs which highlights the most salient features and buildings of that particular spot is also provided. This section is located on the right-hand side of the page, and it is augmented by a collection of YouTube videos which you can watch anytime.

In addition to that, when you key in the name of a city and the Google Map is displayed, you will be able to access the current Wikipedia page on that location.

All in all, this startup gathers together several resources in the same space, and as such it stands as a useful source of information that is certain to make traveling easier and suppler.
